
Locale 44.2 (16.7.99)

 New tooltype MAP. Set the path of the world map image (default is
PROGDIR:worldmap). The user may select another image but it must have
the same width and height as the original map and the same projection.

 One betatester claimed serial output. Didn't find it. Some classes
makes serial output but for every prefs tool, not only locale

Locale 44.3 (31.7.99)

 added stack extension

Locale 44.4 (4.8.99)

 selecting a new country stored wrong country name in prefs. fixed

Locale 44.6 (17.8.99)

 added close gadget

 added seperator line

 modified Save/Use/Cancel layout

 The map scroller is not attached to the window if the window shows the
  full map.

Locale 44.7 (20.8.99)

 added some code to make selected language and country visible in lists.

Locale 44.9 (16.9.99)

 the Country list loads flaggs from LOCALE:Flaggs/Countries/.

 changed the project icon name to def_locale_prefs

Locale 44.10 (22.9.99)

 fixed a typo "Flaggs" -> "Flags"

Locale 44.11 (24.9.99)

 fixed some bugs and enforcer hits with low memory situations

Locale 44.15 (30.9.99)

 listbrowser gadget has problems with "spacing" attribute. Because I am
  not sure if we can fix it before release I set spacing to 0.

--- OS 3.5 release ---

Locale 44.18 (17.11.99)

